# PostHog analytics. Get the project key from app.posthog.com -> Project settings -> Project API key.
# Public envs (PUBLIC_ prefix) are exposed to the browser at build time — only put public client-side
# keys here. PostHog project API keys are designed to be public.
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=
PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com
